text: Anna Turova (born 31 July 1990) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites == * anna turova, getty Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
